# Fetching a Single Resource

Example:

```tsx
export default async function Post() {

    const response =
        await fetch(
            "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1"
        );

    const post =
        await response.json();

    return (
        <article>

            <h1>
                {post.title}
            </h1>

            <p>
                {post.body}
            </p>

        </article>
    );
}
```

