# The Fast Way

Instead:

```tsx
export default async function Dashboard() {

    const [
        users,
        posts,
        comments
    ] = await Promise.all([
        fetchUsers(),
        fetchPosts(),
        fetchComments()
    ]);

    return (
        <div>
            Dashboard
        </div>
    );
}
```

